videos.description: Naji Marshall tosses a lob ahead to Jaxson Hayes who goes up to flush an easy dunk to cap the Pelicans' fast break.

videos.description: Lonzo Ball throws a backdoor alley-oop pass to Zion Williamson who stuffs down the easy two-handed dunk to give the Pelicans a 74-52 lead over the Magic at halftime. (edited)
